This paper is about video captioning, which involves understanding the content of videos and generating natural language descriptions. This task is related to computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper proposes a new approach that involves object detection and spatio-temporal representations, which are also relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
